#

Beetroot Borscht with Sour Cream

60 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

soupvegetarianheartycomfort food

Description

A vibrant beet soup enriched with earthy flavors, served warm with a dollop of creamy sour cream for a delightful contrast.

Ingredients

  • beetroots: 4 medium, peeled and diced
  • carrots: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • potatoes: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 1/2 small head, shredded
  • sour cream: to serve
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
